Package org.fluentjdbc

Class DbContextInsertBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.fluentjdbc.DbContextInsertBuilder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DatabaseUpdatable<DbContextInsertBuilder>
    public class DbContextInsertBuilder
extends Object
implements DatabaseUpdatable<DbContextInsertBuilder>
    Generate INSERT statements by collecting field names and parameters. Support autogeneration of primary keys. Example: 
     DbContextTable table = context.table("database_test_table");
 try (DbContextConnection ignored = context.startConnection(dataSource)) {
     Long id = table.insert()
      .setPrimaryKey("id", (Long)null)
      .setField("name", "Something")
      .setField("code", 102)
      .execute();
 }
